{"word":"G2282 - θάλπω - thálpō - thal'-po - Cherish","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θάλπω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">thálpō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">thal'-po</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Cherish</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - காப்பாற்று"},{"paragraph":"1. to warm, keep warm"},{"paragraph":"2. to cherish with tender love, to foster with tender care"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably akin to <b>&#x03B8;&#x03B1;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03C9;</b> <b>thallo&#x0304;</b> (to <i>warm</i>); to <i>brood</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>foster:</i> - cherish.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}